These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
There 7 different types of food: cranberry, grapefruit, carrot, banana, eggplant, lettuce, cabbage
7 different games are played: go, monopoly, backgammon, mah-jongg, scrabble, chess, canasta
 1. the person eating banana is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 2. the person playing scrabble is the person eating banana##1
 3. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 4. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 5. the person eating carrot is in the middle##1
 6. the person playing go is on the far left##1
 7. the person eating eggplant is the person playing go##1
 8. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
10. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
11. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Food           | eggplant | banana | grapefruit | carrot | cranberry | lettuce | cabbage |
| Game   | go    | scrabble   | mah-jongg      | chess | backgammon    | monopoly    | canasta         |

