.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
City: colone, london, paris, prague, edinburgh, new-york, rome
There are 7 different favourite colors: blood-red, ebony, mauve, brown, green, emerald, chestnut
 1. the person who likes green is the person traveling to prague##1
 2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
 3. the person who likes emerald is on the far right##1
 4. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
 5. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
 6. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
 7. the person who likes green is in the middle##1
 8. the person who likes green is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 9. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
10. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| City          | colone | london | edinburgh | prague | new-york | rome | paris |
| Color   | ebony      | mauve   | brown   | green      | blood-red       | chestnut       | emerald     |

