.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffeeade, fanta, coffee, sprite, cola, mirinda, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: r&b, soul, pop, d&b, hip-hop, ambient, classical
 1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the fan of classical##1
 3. the fan of soul is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 4. the person drinking coffeeade is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 5. the fan of r&b is the person drinking cola##1
 6. the fan of pop is on the right of the fan of soul##1
 7. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of pop##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is the fan of d&b##1
10. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
11. the fan of d&b is in the middle##1
12. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Beverage   | fanta | cola     | coffee  | mirinda       | coffeeade       | hot-chocolate  | sprite   |
| Music-Genre    | ambient  | r&b | classical | d&b | soul | pop | hip-hop |

