 9. the person traveling to hamburg is the pilot##1
10. the pilot is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
11. the architect is the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| City   | boston    | hannover     | berlin     | hamburg      | edinburgh | new-york      | prague     |
| Job   | project-manager | police-officer | dancer | pilot | architect | librarian | mechanic |

