.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: trance, country, electronic, d&b, ambient, techno, rock
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: lacrosse, sailing, parkour, basketball, swimming, ice-hockey, tennis
 1. the fan of country is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in the middle##1
 4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 5. the person who's sport is swimming is the fan of techno##1
 6. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the fan of rock##1
 8. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of country##1
 9. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
10. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Music-Genre   | country | electronic | techno     | d&b | rock | ambient | trance |
| Sport     | tennis   | parkour    | swimming | ice-hockey     | lacrosse         | basketball     | sailing        |

