 3. the modern house is on the right of the russian##1
 4. the indian is on the left of the chinese##1
 5. the dutch is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 6. the tower house is on the left of the craftsman house##1
 7. the art-deco house is in the middle##1
 8. the futuristic house is on the left of the american##1
 9. the palace house is on the right of the dutch##1
10. the futuristic house is on the left of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| House    | futuristic | tower   | craftsman | art-deco | ranch-style  | modern | palace |
| Nationality   | colombian   | american | indian | chinese     | russian | dutch | malaysian   |

