.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-8::.
7 different games are played: billiard, whist, scrabble, bridge, canasta, backgammon, snooker
7 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, hamster, bird, hedgehog, guinea-pig, dog
 1. the person playing canasta is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 2. the owner of the dog is in the middle##1
 3. the person playing whist is the owner of the hamster##1
 4. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 6. the person playing scrabble is the owner of the bird##1
 7. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 8. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is in the middle##1
10. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |       4       |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Game       | whist   | bridge | snooker | backgammon | billiard     | scrabble | canasta |
| Pet   | hamster | guinea-pig      | cat        | dog         | chinchilla | bird     | hedgehog |

