 3. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is in the middle##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person watching satire movies##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is the person watching western movies##1
 7. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 8. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
11. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person watching western movies##1

