7 different games are played: backgammon, go, scrabble, monopoly, poker, snooker, billiard
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person playing go##1
 2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 7. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is in the middle##1
 9. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person playing poker##1
10. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |     5      |     6      |    7     |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing    | photography    | fishing   | dancing | card-games | magic-tricks | puzzles   |
| Game    | scrabble | poker | billiard | snooker  | backgammon       | monopoly     | go |

